hopobject.body: We need someone with qualifications e bun climinax A good article . Brazil is indeed worried about cheap Chinese imports which are starting to have an adverse effect on sales of local produce . The latter tend to be quite expensive due to the protectionist policy of Brazil . To make matters worse Argentina , once a huge trade partner , has begun to restrict imports . The last meeting between Presidents Kirchner and Rousseff was a complete failure . In fact Rousseff left a day early . Also worried by the ” Bolivarian ” stance now adopted by Argentina . No wonder Brazil is now looking fir deals with EU and USA !
